text.section:
This section applies to a bond or other evidence of indebtedness that:
has a fixed term and rate of interest;
is held by an insurer;
is amply secured; and
is not in default as to principal or interest.

section.section:
A bond or other evidence of indebtedness subject to this section may be valued:
if purchased at par, at the par value; or
if purchased above or below par:
